            Coloured wedding dresses are on trend: Designer Ogake Mosomi
            Could the traditional white wedding dress be a thing of the past?Ogake Mosomi from Nairobi in Kenya designs colourful wedding dresses and says the demand is growing.In this BBC Africa One Minute Story, she explains why.Video journalists: Gloria Achieng and Ashley Lime.
                
